s an effective tool to monitor\nthe onset of the two-channel Kondo effect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Mar 2016 18:32:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 25 Jun 2016 14:34:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-28"}
