 masses of the stars in our simulation do not appear limited by\ntheir own luminosities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Mar 2016 20:27:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Apr 2016 18:14:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
